        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Add some flare to your knives and blades collection with the ASR Outdoor 19\" Tomahawk Peace Pipe.<br/><br/>This unique axe has two different functions. It features a real tomahawk blade constructed of durable stainless steel that wont rust, and it also works as a classic peace pipe. It comes with a leather wrapped handle that gives it an authentic look will providing comfort and grip while in use. <br/><br/>The axe head itself features a 4 inch blade, and both the head and the pipe are attached securely to the wooden handle. The overall 19 inch length makes it a great size to display on your mantle or in a display case in your home. It also comes with a lanyard and real feathers to complete the look. This replica peace pipe is a must-have addition to any weapon collection.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
